# Browser RPC for lock transactions (send tx still uses wallet + ConnectionProvider).
# Balance reads use /api/balance with server SOLANA_RPC_URL — no VITE_ var required on Vercel.
# For faster local tx simulation, set to your Helius/QuickNode URL:
# VITE_SOLANA_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
